{"content": "I need to multiply 366 \u00d7 832 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 366 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 366\u2081\u2081 = 3\u00d711\u00b2 + 6\u00d711\u00b9 + 6\u00d711\u2070\n- = 3\u00d7121 + 6\u00d711 + 6\u00d71\n- = 363 + 66 + 6\n- = 435\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 832 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 832\u2081\u2081 = 8\u00d711\u00b2 + 3\u00d711\u00b9 + 2\u00d711\u2070\n- = 8\u00d7121 + 3\u00d711 + 2\u00d71\n- = 968 + 33 + 2\n- = 1003\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 435 \u00d7 1003 = 436,305\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 436,305 back to base 11**\n- 436,305 \u00f7 11 = 39,664 R 1\n- 39,664 \u00f7 11 = 3,606 R 0\n- 3,606 \u00f7 11 = 327 R 9\n- 327 \u00f7 11 = 29 R 8\n- 29 \u00f7 11 = 2 R 7\n- 2 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 2\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 278901\n\n278901", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 393}